HEADWORD: Flobert
<hw>Flo"bert</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Gun.)</fld> <def>A
small cartridge designed for target shooting; -- sometimes called
<altname>ball cap</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Flobert rifle</b></col>, <cd>a rifle adapted to the use
of floberts.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

